{"tid":946463,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"地區鬼故","createTime":"2018-12-18T14:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T15:36:29.000Z","uid":216662,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1088475f5bec8cf52a3471fb6cb595465dea7bad","tid":946463,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:06:29.000Z","msg":"南丫島<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （真人真事）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中5放暑假嗰陣有個同學叫阿輝南丫島原居民，話屋企無人，暑假可以去佢袓屋度燒嘢食同玩過夜。<br />\n<br />\n到嗰日十幾個男女同學一齊坐船到南丫島玩，落船一路行一路傾玩咩同買咩燒嘢食嗰陣，望到個阿伯用支拐杖撩坑渠邊個草叢，阿輝就扮勁咁問阿伯有無嘢要幫手？<br />\n阿伯就話搵緊個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地成班已經覺得阿伯好有問題<br />\n但阿輝仲問:點會喺草叢搵仔㗎<br />\n阿伯就話：如果我個仔未死好似你咁大個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿輝仲唔識死仲想傾，我地成班人捉佢先肯走去買燒烤嘢。。。<br />\n<br />\n買完到夜晚啲人就分頭行事，有啲打機，有啲就打牌，有幾個就去透燒烤爐，到個爐着咗就叫哂啲人一齊埋嚟燒，全部人嚟哂但淨係唔見阿輝，之後有個同學話海中心有個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知係咪阿輝呢。叫極佢都唔應，慶慶地同另外個同學一齊行出去叫佢，好彩好淺水，但一行到見到阿輝坐咗係度食沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇到我同個fd仆乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nつづく"},{"pid":"3841fc7d0bd0a3e65b048048e0e90a07a49706c7","tid":946463,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2e2dd80c96a890f89fd206446c3eec27388ec7","tid":946463,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3841fc7d0bd0a3e65b048048e0e90a07a49706c7","tid":946463,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"