08,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/7-21-2016/MpLs6n.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F7-21-2016%2FMpLs6n.gif&h=ffaa702f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邊個阿輝得人驚d?"}]}